Description
-----------
Overlays "cinema-bars" over the live picture

 - keys 'Up/Down' toggles top/bottom bar
 - keys 'Right/Left' increase/decrease barheight of actual visible bar(s)
 - keys 'Back/Blue' exit plugin 
 - key  'Red' close/open screen
 - key  'Ok' close screen and exit plugin
 - keys 'Green/Yellow' change color of bars
 